  "prompt": "Where online can I use my Maestro card?",
  "response": "Maestro cards are widely accepted at various online merchants, but acceptance can vary by region and specific retailer. Here are some popular online platforms where Maestro cards are commonly accepted:\n\n1. **Amazon** - In many countries, Amazon accepts Maestro cards for purchases.\n2. **eBay** - Depending on the seller, Maestro can be used on eBay.\n3. **ASOS** - The online fashion retailer often accepts Maestro cards.\n4. **Booking.com** - For booking hotels and accommodations.\n5. **Expedia** - For travel-related purchases like flights and hotels.\n\nTo ensure your Maestro card is accepted, it's a good idea to:\n- Check the payment section of the website before making a purchase.\n- Contact the customer support of the online store if you're unsure.\n\nKeep in mind that some online merchants might not accept Maestro cards, especially in regions where they are less common. Always verify the accepted payment methods before completing your transaction.",
